# 💬 Real-Time Chat App

A full-stack real-time chat application built with the **MERN stack** (MongoDB, Express.js, React, Node.js), using **Socket.IO** for instant messaging and **MVC architecture** for clean project structure.

## 📌 Features

- 🔐 **User Authentication**
  - Register & login with JWT-based authentication
  - Passwords securely hashed with bcrypt

- 💬 **Real-Time Messaging**
  - Instant chat powered by Socket.IO
  - Online user tracking

- 👥 **One-to-One Chat**
  - Create personal conversations
  - Chat history stored in MongoDB

- 📄 **MVC Architecture**
  - Clean separation of concerns: Models, Controllers, Routes

- 🧭 **Modern UI**
  - React + Tailwind CSS (or your preferred framework)
  - Responsive design for mobile and desktop

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

**Frontend:**
- React.js
- Axios
- Socket.IO client

**Backend:**
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB + Mongoose
- Socket.IO
- JWT & Bcrypt
- MVC Architecture

## 🗂️ Project Structure

```bash
📁 client/
  ├── src/
      ├── components/
      ├── pages/
      ├── context/
      ├── services/
📁 server/
  ├── controllers/
  ├── models/
  ├── routes/
  ├── utils/
  ├── config/
  └── server.js
